cc:Work.dc:description: This is a tag with a blue label. The design is inspired by the Mark James "tag_blue" icon from his Silk library. There are some light bevels, shadows, and a "gloss" layer, but it's a very simple design overall. Unfortunately, there are a few dozen unused gradient definitions that increase the file size a bit that I haven't had time to hand-edit out of the file (shakes fist at Inkscape devs). Attribution requested, but not required. I'm just curious to see if anyone else finds this icon useful.
